Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/4xx: Fix error return path in ppc4xx_msi_probe()
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.18.9
Git-commit: 6e0495c2e8ac39b1aad0a4588fe64413ce9028c0

[ Upstream commit 6e0495c2e8ac39b1aad0a4588fe64413ce9028c0 ]

